organization.description: This is a group to collect and curate high value and high quality datasets related to international development and aid.
organization.title: International Development Data
organization.name: international-development

name: ifpri-food-security-portal
notes: Contains over 40 indicators related to food security, commodity prices, economics, and human well-being. Much of this data is available for every country in the world and goes back over 50 years. We draw from public, authoritative data sources like the World Bank, the FAO, UNICEF, and others, as well as IFPRI's own data.
title: IFPRI Food Security Portal
